text: Arthur Vincent (born 30 September 1999) is a French rugby union player. His position is centre and he currently plays for Montpellier in the Top 14. ==International Honours== France (U20) *Six Nations Under 20s Championship winners: 2018 *World Rugby Under 20 Championship winners (2): 2018, 2019 ==References== ==External links== *Montpellier HR profile *L'Équipe profile Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:French rugby union players Category:France international rugby union players Category:Montpellier Hérault Rugby players Category:Rugby union centres
